Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:22.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}あなたは　二度とは帰ってこない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:28.20,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}僕を壊すほど大きな　傷を残して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:33.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}繋がる温もり　思い出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:39.85,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}塗り潰されたキャンバス　消えたパフューム
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:45.82,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}滅びてしまうことが　運命でも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:50.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}僕は信じていたい　愛を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:57.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4\fs20\pos(812,8.8)\fsp15}まじ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:57.32,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4\pos(640,35)}痛みは絆を求めて　世界と交配わる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:22:02.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}震える指　隠して　明日を目指す
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:08.83,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}あなたがもし望むのなら　命も捧げる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}汚れたトリガー引く時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:17.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}Stay with me, I'll change your destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:21.22,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}TO WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:22.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}你已再也不会回到我的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:28.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}留下的伤痕  让我近乎崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:33.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}相连的温暖  令我不愿回想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:39.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}被涂满的画布  消散的香水味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:45.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}即使走向毁灭是无可避免的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:50.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}我也愿意相信  这份爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:57.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}在痛苦中寻求羁绊  与世界缠绕交织
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:22:02.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}隐藏起指间的颤抖  朝着明天的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:08.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}如果这是你的愿望  我愿将性命相交
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}当扣下污浊的扳机之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:17.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}你与我同在  我将改变你的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:21.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}向着这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TXT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和那时比起来好走多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就是那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,致我的挚友  周防天音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在读这封信就说明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事故已经过去了数年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而你也已经冷静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定很想知道这里究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才打开了这个箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先把结果先简单地告知于你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:00:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部人都病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原因是广冈同学所患有的皮肤疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家服用了含有毒素的汤之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都患上了急性内脏疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后全都病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  没有吃那些肉的你得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就结果而言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许真正救你的人是广冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  就我对你的了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定认为自己获救是多亏了挺身而出的好友风见一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,并且一边流着泪一边满怀感激吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么作为你救命恩人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我的弟弟身陷痛苦之中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能帮助他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的弟弟雄二既胆小又爱哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要说优点的话  就只有为人比较温柔这点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:02:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过对我而言  却是我无可替代的可爱弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我仅有的牵挂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能守护我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  要是还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,期盼我们的再次重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你人生最好的挚友  风见一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬到底怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活着吗  还是死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这封信的确很有一姬的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是敌不过一姬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里和当初一样  几乎没有改变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沿着那个方向走三个小时就可以抵达公路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也得当时有那条路才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话我还是很害怕你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只是一味地逃避并不能解决问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我放弃逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「只有我活了下来  原谅我」这种话我不会说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道想要获得原谅这个想法就是很厚颜无耻的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不会道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换  之后我会一直感谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坂下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莳菜打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么呢  周防天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等着你回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有在听吗  天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢  是坂下千秋的父亲坂下启二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坂下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫坂下  是天音的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坂下部长的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为遗属代表来制裁你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.00,TXTD,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(192,546)}1小时前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底鲔鱼超人究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要说几次你才懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鲔鱼超人是守护人类和平的正义战士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的这些听多少遍都不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是人还是鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊小姐  出门的时候要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  怎么说我也是死了的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问周防天音在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐和爸爸开车出去兜风了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我让他们带我去  结果被拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人要真干了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀  去约会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫坂下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  各位能先换下衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要袭击大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要找的人是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之麻烦你快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁着你朋友还平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的金发
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快把手机拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  为什么要拿走我的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方携带着武器  支援就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是需要我们出马的事件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去拜托警察如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警察介入的话  由美子还活着的事就会暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被榊道昭发现的话  不是会变得很麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  作战会在你的权限范围内进行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,学校真是棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千秋如果还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定在这样的教室里学习
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友一起增进友谊  享受着人生才对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事情我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你做这种事又有什么用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说我做的都是白费力气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能明白突然失去女儿的父亲是什么心情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是多么的心痛  多么痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这不是一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一  清  二  楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  这是怎么回事啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}（清扫中  禁止进入）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人潜伏在三楼的空教室内
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,武器是猎枪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,窗户被窗帘所遮挡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,内部情况不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是打扫垃圾  潜入各种地方做清扫活动的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的脏活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别想多余的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人和人质在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一般情况  我们会从窗户对他进行狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  请别在学生面前进行狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想办法和他谈判一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校舍四周被高墙所包围
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,附近没有高层建筑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,后方是大海  就狙击而言非常困难
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次就用其他的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能狙击的话  把他引诱出来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个能狙击的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,入学第一天所看到的  换气用的小窗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪里进行射击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高台上有个灯塔  从那里瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离这可有900米啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点进行确认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是从灯塔传来的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,射界最多只有10厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,射界15厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,4年前在射界15厘米的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狙击了躲在被障碍物包围的餐厅内的恐怖分子的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是麻子的传说之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把犯人引到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家便不会看到狙击的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你很清楚我的技术吧  千鹤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请千万别让学生们受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把犯人引诱到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他不用右边数过来的第二个便池
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会进入射程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就想办法让他用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人质中有一位海军陆战队员  她能帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摩尔斯电码？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三楼  男子  厕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最右边的便池  破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么  完全不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然收到了信号就要行动  这就是海军陆战队之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为紧张  肚子变得好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛得快要裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要  要拉出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大便还是会不断漏出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不想我用它糊你一脸的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就快点带我去厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你没法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,满满也要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别  满满你就别跟过来了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊  我也憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见先生  犯人跟小莳和满大小姐一起去走廊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目前我们四人没有受到危害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有劳报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧解决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这可是男厕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,进单间不就都一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我要去女…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这解决吧  这里最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是什么嗜好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然接了命令  不过这东西要怎么破坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,满满干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,队员完成了任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊  你磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点过来的话你的好朋友们就得死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就去  马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,周防同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再给大家添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音  把瓶装水带上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,争取让坂下多喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你能控制坂下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点用对话拖延时间直到那家伙起尿意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的交给我就行  相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临  周防小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些给她们补充水分  也有你的份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请放了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么急  先换上校服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,换完我们再商量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,商量？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要商量什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家千晶被分尸埋在了冰冷的泥土下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而你却在新同学的关怀中享受校园生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还交上了男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是牺牲了朋友活下来的丑恶毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:15:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你有那么一丝悔改之心就证明给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你愿意在这让我射死  我就放了那四人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若你选择让我射死她们四人的话  我就放了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  你要不要再次牺牲朋友苟且偷生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能射死我你就满足了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就赶快放了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,周防同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋  竟敢这么对天姐你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴  白痴  怎么可能让你死得那么轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,周防同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来嘛  起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么做完全就是拿她撒气来泄恨而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能怪天姐  遇上那种事谁能顾那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论事情如何  你都没权利惩罚天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  你可真是交了一群好朋友啊天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还是让你们一起去死比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃什么把身材养这么棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准逃  你这毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,JB  情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情况不明  你那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸的手机挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要突入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  继续等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:17:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐  你  把千晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我过来  在杀你之前先爽一爽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我走快点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见先生  天音小姐被带走了  请求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我马上就插你个爽  给我等着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,JB  目标进入射界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水喝太多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  咦  咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等  畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狙击成功  请求捕捉犯人和救出人质
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千晶  千晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,射界10厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我追上你了吗  麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  这不是天音小姐的错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也惹过不少麻烦  彼此彼此啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  到底是谁救了我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然周防小姐受了一点伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了  风见同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鹤  不对  校长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道这算不算普通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我可以肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是我的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  不准抢跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事我就回房上网了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又上网？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定又是通宵收黄图
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想收就收关你什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  她承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准无视我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:29.59,zhushi,,0,0,0,,八重山群岛：琉球群岛西部的群岛，位于钓鱼台群岛以南，宫古群岛以西。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:29.59,TXTD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs25\an1\pos(264,575.333)}1年后\N八重山群岛  与那国附近海域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警告目的不明舰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是日本海上保安厅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,贵舰涉嫌侵犯日本领海  请立即停船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重复一遍  请立即停船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:40.22,TXTGb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fs60\pos(640,548)}下回预告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:45.99,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7\fad(200,200)\blur4}话说  我们基本上都不知道\N有关雄二过去的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:44.27,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an3\fad(200,200)\blur4}站起来  站起来啊\N鲔鱼超人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:47.39,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an1\fad(200,200)\blur4}什么  谁习惯孤零零了\N而且我本来就不是孤零零
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:47.56,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8\fad(200,200)\blur4}现在将开始加油和交换人质
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:51.67,TXTGa,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an4\fad(200,200)\blur4\pos(68,249.333)}简历我看过了\N这年代不至于\N还需要用手写的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:52.17,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8\fad(200,200)\blur4}第一个由你来上\N拜托你用第一发\N使犯人丧失行动能力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:52.47,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an2\fad(200,200)\blur4}军人不允许说不可能这个词\N没有军人做不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:54.63,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an3\fad(200,200)\blur4}嘿  能听到吗回旋镖\N观测装置设置完毕  资料传到你PC上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:56.72,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an2\fad(200,200)\blur4}我专门把你从日本叫过来\N可别给我丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:59.32,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7\fad(200,200)\blur4}我小岭幸\N想给繁忙至极的风见先生\N献上自己的微薄之力\N正在为其打扫房间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:56.70,TXTGa,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an4\fad(200,200)\blur4\pos(36,210.667)}莫非是找到了发霉的内裤？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:23:01.09,TXTGa,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an6\fad(200,200)\blur4\pos(1246.67,464)}不  是更惊人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:23:00.56,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an1\fad(200,200)\blur4}解除射击限制\N重复一遍  解除射击限制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:02.53,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an3\fad(200,200)\blur4}你姐姐的死\N有一些可疑之处
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.33,0:23:06.14,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}哟  小弟\N这位小姐一口日语  在生什么气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:07.22,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7\fad(200,200)\blur4}你总是这样什么都不说\N要是觉得难受你可以跟我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:05.05,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an4\fad(200,200)\blur4}呐  雄二\N来玩接球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:07.43,TXTGa,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an6\fad(200,200)\blur4\pos(1229.33,450.667)}一只蚂蚁也不要放过\N赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:09.86,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an3\fad(200,200)\blur4}什么  你说这位小姐\N年龄比我大？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:19.82,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an1\fad(200,200)\blur4}我会这般深爱你这个弟弟\N从遗传基因的角度上来看肯定是正确的\N要不就是遗传基因发生了异常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:12.15,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an4\fad(200,200)\blur4}杀了吗  哈哈哈哈哈\N你挺能干的嘛雄二  你真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:19.04,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an4\fad(200,200)\blur4}这就对了  雄二  你做对了\N这才是人类与生俱来的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:18.95,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}对于您救了我这件事我非常感谢\N不过  我想抗议一下  您就不能选择其他更好一点的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:21.36,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur4}早上好  小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:24.72,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur4}咦  是小弟弟  吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:32.10,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}或许我是想在普通的学校  过一过普通的学生生活
